<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>HI Mallory, I purchased the Petkit Eversweet3 late October 2020. It has since had the pump fail. I have not had any luck with Petkit responding to customer service requests to purchase a pump and also noted that many recent reviews on Amazon for this product are showing the same problem. Many have the unit run for 3-4 months and then the pump fails and no customer service and no parts available. I plan to steer clear of Petkit as a company based on this, which is sad. My cat and I both really liked the Eversweet3 and now I have to go find something else that will work and not cause more work than it saves.</p>
</section>
