<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>Hello! These reviews are super helpful. I’m inclined to go with the PetKit Eversweet, but Catit also makes a Pixi fountain that is super cute and has some of the same features &#8211; quiet, automatic shutoff &#8211; and one model has a steel bowl option. I’d be very interested to know if there any reason that the Pixi was excluded, that would make the Eversweet a better choice? In any case, thanks very much!</p>
